                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>A new report has found that eczema symptoms cause negative impacts on the physical and mental health of patients.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;AbbVie in collaboration with the Eczema Association of New Zealand is proud to release results of the largest survey on the lived experience of New Zealanders with eczema.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;The survey reveals the daily struggle for Kiwis who face significant physical, emotional, economic, and social impacts caused by eczema.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Access the report here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://bit.ly/3MEcIT2&quot; title=&quot;ttps://bit.ly/3MEcIT2&quot;>https://bit.ly/3MEcIT2&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;For information about eczema talk to your doctor. &lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;TAPS BG4243&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
